-        "totalCoresUsed": 4,
-        "maxTotalRAMSize": 51200,
-        "maxServerGroups": 10,
-        "totalServerGroupsUsed": 2,
-        "maxServersPerServerGroups": 10,
-
-    }
-
-  }
-
-}
-
-Change in the response of ServerGroup API:
-
-Create can now return 413 "Quota Exceeded for server groups"
-
